 transportes aéreos algeco scotsman arch coal caesars entertainment energy xxi kenya airways oi sa samson resources iheartmedia creditors and sports authority creditors contents  history and background  leadership  business and competitors  references history and backgroundedit in  pjt partners inc was created from a merger of the advisory arm of the blackstone group which had operated for thirty years and pjt capital lp a strategic advisory firm founded by paul j taubman in  pjt partners first day of trading was on october   on the same day it became publicly traded listing on the new york stock exchange nyse under the symbol pjt on its first day of trading pjt had  employees and  partners blackstone’s decision to do the spinoff was largely driven by the conflicts of interest that arose between blackstone’s advisory services business and its investing businesses including private equity real estate investing and hedge funds in march  pjt partner andrew caspersen was arrested on federal charges of securities and wire fraud federal prosecutors allege that caspersen engaged in a scheme to defraud investors of up to  million caspersen was quickly fired and pjt released a statement saying that it was cooperating with the authorities and was stunned and outraged to hear about the allegations leadershipedit paul j taubman has served as the chairman and chief executive of pjt partners since its inception in  and was the founder of its predecessor firm pjt capital lp in  he previously spent approximately  years at morgan stanley where he was copresident of institutional securities bloomberg news reported that taubman was the secondhighestpaid us executive of  after patrick soonshiong earning  million in awarded pay in  before the firm began operations taubman hired a number of senior european bankers to lead pjt partners european operation soon after the firm was founded former nba commissioner david j stern joined the firm as a senior adviser business and competitorsedit the firm is organized across three business lines strategic advisory handles ma capital markets advisory spinoffs private placements structured products and other transactions restructuring  special situations handles debtor advisory creditor advisory outofcourt solutions distressed ma and expert witness testimony the park hill group provides services for private equity real estate hedge funds and secondary advisory services the firm competes with all investment banks that provide strategic advisory services referencesedit  a b blackstone successfully completes spinoff of pjt partners business wire october     pjt partners contact pjt partners retrieved march     rothnie david january   takeover veteran paul taubman aims high with pjt partners institutional investor magazine   june  investor presentation pdf   pjt partnerscompany profilevaultcom vault retrieved    a b c michael j de la merced paul taubman taking reins of investment bank with blackstone ties new york times september    a b massoudi arash fontanellakhan james september   taubman boutique jumps straight to ipo financial times   oran olivia march   many blackstone ma bankers expected to depart ahead of spin off to taubman reuters   a b c alexandra stevenson  matthew goldstein wall street scion is accused of faking investments new york times march    executive profile paul j taubman bloomberg business march     de la merced michael j september   paul taubman taking reins of investment bank with blackstone ties new york times   a b demos telis demos october   paul j taubmans ma boutique to go public wall street journal   anders melin  caleb melby with  million award doctor tops banker in  ceo pay bloomberg news april    arash massoudi taubman lures more dealmakers to boutique financial times april    michael j de la merced david stern former nba commissioner joins paul taubmans firm new york times october    a b c d pjt partners linkedin retrieved april     boston claire november   greenhill targets europe